---
import { SITE_NAME, SITE_DOMAIN, CONTACT_EMAIL, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../utils/constants';
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-950">
  <!-- Domain Acquisition CTA -->
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-8 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-950 border border-slate-700 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14 text-center">
        <div class="uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-gem mr-2"></i>DOMAIN AVAILABLE FOR ACQUISITION
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-4">
          {SITE_DOMAIN}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-1 text-sm">
          {SITE_DESCRIPTION}
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          This premium .com domain is available for visionary founders, AI-native brands, strategic investors, and creative technology companies seeking category-defining positioning.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}?subject=Domain%20Acquisition%20-%20${SITE_DOMAIN}`}
             class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-3 px-9 py-4 rounded-3xl bg-white text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100 active:bg-slate-200 transition-all font-semibold text-base shadow-xl shadow-indigo-500/30">
            <span>Acquire This Domain</span>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope group-active:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform"></i>
          </a>
          <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}?subject=Serious%20Inquiry%20-%20${SITE_DOMAIN}`}
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-900 transition-all font-medium text-base">
            <span>Serious Inquiries</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-600 max-w-sm mx-auto">
          All inquiries are confidential. We work with serious buyers and their representatives.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom bar -->
  <div class="border-t border-slate-800 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-y-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
        <div>{SITE_DOMAIN} — A premium digital asset</div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
          <a href="/robots.txt" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Robots</a>
          <a href="/sitemap-index.xml" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Sitemap</a>
          <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`} class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Contact</a>
        </div>
        <div>&copy; 2026 &bull; All rights reserved</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 text-center text-[10px] text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        This website is for demonstration and informational purposes only. It does not constitute an offer of services,
        a commitment to deploy, or a guarantee of outcomes. All statistics, projections, and references to specific
        technologies are based on publicly available information as of the date shown and are subject to change.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
